data.title: Front Range Arborist
data.meta_description: Front Range Arborist is proud to serve Colorado Springs and surrounding areas with a full range of tree, shrub, fire, and pest control services.
data.text:
Consultation: Professional arborist advice on caring for your valued landscape trees and shrubs.

Tree Pruning: Crown thinning, dead-wood removal, and structural pruning. From young trees to mature trees, we will prescribe only what your tree needs.

Stump and Tree Removal: We have the experience and equipment to handle any size of tree stump.

Shrub Pruning: Maintenance of shrubs of any size, shape, or species. From shearing for a formal look to natural pruning for a softer look.

Fire Mitigation: Fire mitigation services remove fuels around your house that can create increased heat and exposure to your home in the event of a wildland fire. Wildland fires include grass fires, brush fires, and forest fires. The impact of these fires can be minimized or mitigated by creating a defensible space and taking other actions to reduce the intensity of the fire and help fire crews fight fires that may threaten your home.

Fertilization: We will prescribe the proper nutrients to maintain the health and vigor of your trees and shrubs.

Winter Water: Coloradoâ€™s dry winters are the #1 killer of landscaped trees and shrubs. Take advantage of our Winter Water program to help valuable trees and shrubs grow and survive the winter.

Pest Control Services: We can propose a plant health program to control insect problems on your trees and shrubs. Our applicators are licensed through the Colorado Department of Agriculture.

Tree Preservation: Our tree preservation services protect valuable trees and shrubs before, during, and after construction.

Contact Front Range Arborists for tree services in Colorado Springs, CO

Based in Colorado Springs, CO, Front Range Arborists offers arborist services including pest control and beetle prevention, fire mitigation, tree removal, tree trimming, and more tree services.
